            <h1>David P. Boder Interviews Lena Kuechler; September 8, 1946; Bellevue, France</h1>
                        <ul class="transcripts">
    <li class="interview_home">
        <a href="interviewee?doc=kuechlerL">
            Interview homepage
        </a>
